<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220459>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Neolucanus baongocae new species ♂ (Holotype) dorsal (a) and ventral (b), Bidoup Mountain, Lam Dong province, central Vietnam (scale bar = 1 cm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220459/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220464>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6 – 8. Neolucanus baongocae new species. 6, mentum and submentum of holotype; 7, mandibles of large male; 8, male genitalia (holotype), ventral (a), lateral (b), and dorsal (c)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220464/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220460>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Neolucanus baongocae new species ♀ (paratype), dorsal (a) and ventral (b) (scale bar = 1 cm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220460/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

